packageMeta.name: purescript-birds
packageMeta.description: A collection of bird combinators ported to purescript

declarations.comments:
A combinator - applicator

(a → b) → a → b
`λ f x . f x`
declarations.title: applicator

declarations.comments:
B combinator - bluebird 
S(KS)K
(b → c) → (a → b) → a → c
`λ g f x . g (f x)`
declarations.title: bluebird

declarations.comments:
B' combinator - bluebird prime
BB
(a → c → d) → a → (b → c) → b → d
`λ f x g y . f x (g y)`
declarations.title: bluebird'

declarations.comments:
B1 combinator - blackbird
BBB
(c → d) → (a → b → c) → a → b → d
`λ f g x y . f (g x y)`
declarations.title: blackbird

declarations.comments:
B2 combinator - bunting 
B(BBB)B
(d → e) → (a → b → c → d) → a → b → c → e 
`λ f g x y z . f (g x y z)`
declarations.title: bunting

declarations.comments:
B3 combinator - becard
B(BB)B
(c → d) → (b → c) → (a → b) → a → d
`λ f g h x . f (g (h x))`
declarations.title: becard

declarations.comments:
C combinator - cardinal
S(BBS)(KK)
(a → b → c) → b → a → c
`λ f x y . f y x`
declarations.title: cardinal

declarations.comments:
C' combinator - cardinal prime
S(BBS)(KK)
(c → a → d) → (b → c) → a → b → d
`λ f g x y . f (g y) x`
declarations.title: cardinal'

declarations.comments:
C* combinator - cardinal once removed
BC
(a → c → b → d) → a → b → c → d
`λ f x y z . f x z y`
declarations.title: cardinalstar

declarations.comments:
C** combinator - cardinal twice removed
BC*
(a → b → d → c → e) → a → b → c → d → e
`λ f s t u v . f s t v u`
declarations.title: cardinalstarstar

declarations.comments:
D combinator - dove
BB
(a → c → d) → a → (b → c) → b → d
`λ f x g y . f x (g y)`
declarations.title: dove

declarations.comments:
D1 combinator - dickcissel
B(BB)
(a → b → d → e) → a → b → (c → d) → c → e
`λ f x y g z . f x y (g z)`
declarations.title: dickcissel

declarations.comments:
D2 combinator - dovekie
BB(BB)
(c → d → e) → (a → c) → a → (b → d) → b → e
`λ f g x h z . f (g x) (h z)`
declarations.title: dovekie

declarations.comments:
E combinator - eagle
B(BBB) 
(a → d → e) → a → (b → c → d) → b → c → e
`λ f x g y z . f x (g y z)`
declarations.title: eagle

declarations.comments:
Ê combinator - bald eagle
B(BBB)(B(BBB))
(e → f → g) → (a → b → e) → a → b → (c → d → f) → c → d → g
`λ f g s t h u v . f (g s t) (h u v)`
declarations.title: baldeagle

declarations.comments:
F combinator - finch
ETTET
a → b → (b → a → c) → c
`λ x y f . f y x`
declarations.title: finch

declarations.comments:
F* combinator - finch once removed 
BC*R*
(c → b → a → d) → a → b → c → d
`λ f x y z . f z y x`
declarations.title: finchstar

declarations.comments:
G combinator - goldfinch
BBC
(b → c → d) → (a → c) → a → b → d
`λ f g x y . f y (g x)`
declarations.title: goldfinch

declarations.comments:
H combinator - hummingbird
BW(BC)
(a → b → a → c) → a → b → c 
`λ f x y . f x y x`
declarations.title: hummingbird

declarations.comments:
I combinator - identity bird 
SKK
a → a 
`λ x . x`
declarations.title: idiot

declarations.comments:
I* combinator - id bird once removed
S(SK)
(a → b) → a → b
`λ f x . f x`
declarations.title: idstar

declarations.comments:
I** combinator - id bird twice removed 

(a → b → c) → a → b → c
`λ f x y . f x y`
declarations.title: idstarstar

declarations.comments: Psi combinator - psi bird - `on`
declarations.title: psi

declarations.comments:
J combinator - Jay
B(BC)(W(BC(B(BBB))))
(a → b → b) → a → b → a → b
`λ f x y z . f x (f z y)`
declarations.title: jay

declarations.comments:
Alternative J combinator - Joy

(a → c) → a → b → c
`λf x y . f x`
declarations.title: jalt

declarations.comments:
J' combinator - Joy prime

(a → b → d) → a → b → c → d
`λ f x y z . f x y`
declarations.title: jalt'

declarations.comments:
K combinator - kestrel
K
a → b → a
`λ x y . x`
declarations.title: kestrel

declarations.comments:
Ki combinator - kite (false)
KI
a → b → b
`λ x y . y`
declarations.title: kite

declarations.comments:
Φcombinator - phoenix 

(b → c → d) → (a → b) → (a → c) → a → d
`λ f g h x . f (g x) (h x)`
declarations.title: phoenix

declarations.comments:
Q combinator - queer bird
CB
(a → b) → (b → c) → a → c
`λ f g x . g (f x)`
declarations.title: queer

declarations.comments:
Q1 combinator - quixotic bird
BCB
(b → c) → a → (a → b) → c
`λ f x g . f (g x)`
declarations.title: quixotic

declarations.comments:
Q2 combinator - quizzical bird 
C(BCB)
a → (b → c) → (a → b) → c
`λ x f g . f (g x)`
declarations.title: quizzical

declarations.comments:
Q3 combinator - quircky bird
BT
(a → b) → a → (b → c) → c
`λ f x g . g (f x)`
declarations.title: quirky

declarations.comments:
Q4 combinator - quacky bird
F*B
a → (a → b) → (b → c) → c
`λ x f g . g (f x)`
declarations.title: quacky

declarations.comments:
O combinator - owl
SI 
((a → b) → a) → (a → b) → b
`λ x y . y (x y)`
declarations.title: owl

declarations.comments:
R combinator - robin
BBT
a → (b → a → c) → b → c
`λ x f y . f y x`
declarations.title: robin

declarations.comments:
R* combinator - robin once removed 
C*C*
(b → c → a → d) → a → b → c → d
`λ f x y z . f y z x`
declarations.title: robinstar

declarations.comments:
R** combinator - robin twice removed 
BR*
(a → c → d → b → e) → a → b → c → d → e
`λ f s t u v . f s u v t`
declarations.title: robinstarstar

declarations.comments:
S combinator - starling
S
(a → b → c) → (a → b) → a → c
`λ f g x . f x (g x)`
declarations.title: starling

declarations.comments:
S' combinator - starling prime

(b → c → d) → (a → b) → (a → c) → a → d
`λ f g h x . f (g x) (h x)`
declarations.title: starling'

declarations.comments:
T combinator - thrush
CI
a → (a → b) → b
`λ x f . f x`
declarations.title: thrush

declarations.comments:
V combinator - vireo
BCT
a → b → (a → b → c) → c
`λ x y f . f x y`
declarations.title: vireo

declarations.comments:
V** combinator - vireo twice removed
BV*
(a → c → b → c → e) → a → b → c → c → e
`λ f s t u v . f s v t u`
TODO
declarations.title: vireostarstar

declarations.comments:
W combinator - warbler - omega 
MM
(a → a → b) → a → b
`λ f x . f x x`
declarations.title: warbler

declarations.comments:
W1 combinator - converse warbler 
CW
a → (a → a → b) → b
`λ x f = f x x`
declarations.title: worbler

declarations.comments:
W* combinator - warbler once removed 
BW
(a → b → b → c) → a → b → c
`λ f x y . f x y y`
declarations.title: warblerstar

declarations.comments:
W** combinator - warbler twice removed 
BV*
(a → b → c → c → d) → a → b → c → d
`λ f x y z . f x y z z`
declarations.title: warblerstarstar
